<!DOCTYPE tmc-service-paragraph SYSTEM "../dtd/paragraph-contents.dtd">
<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_51"><name>Engine / Hybrid System</name><section id="_029760"><name>1VD-FTV ENGINE CONTROL</name><ttl id="_0282525"><name>ECD SYSTEM(w/ DPF)</name><para id="RM100000000YZ3K" category="C"><dtccode>P0724</dtccode><dtcname>Brake Switch &quot;B&quot; Circuit High</dtcname><subpara id="RM100000000YZ3K_02" category="03"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><ptxt>This DTC indicates that the stop light switch remains on. When the stop light switch remains on during GO and STOP driving, the ECM interprets this as a fault in the stop light switch. Then the MIL illuminates and the ECM stores the DTC.</ptxt><table type="dtc-explan-table" pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="6"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="2" colwidth="1.42in"/><colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="5" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="6" colwidth="0.70in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Detection Item</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>MIL</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Memory</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P0724</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Brake Switch &quot;B&quot; Circuit High</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>Stop light switch remains on even when vehicle is driven in GO (30 km/h (19 mph) or more) and STOP (less than 3 km/h (1.8 mph)) pattern 5 times.</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Short in stop light switch signal circuit</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Stop light switch assembly</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="mil"><ptxt>Comes on</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="memory"><ptxt>DTC stored</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><table pgwide="1"><title>Related Data List</title><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="3.54in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3.54in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Data List</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P0724</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Stop Light Switch</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YZ3K_03" category="03"><name>CONFIRMATION DRIVING PATTERN</name><content5><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.42in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="5.66in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Drive Pattern</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>P0724</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle"><ptxt>Accelerate the vehicle to 30 km/h (19 mph) or more, depress the brake pedal and decelerate the vehicle to 3 km/h (1.8 mph) or less 5 times.</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YZ3K_04" category="03"><name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name><content5><ptxt>Refer to DTC P0504</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000YXUT"/></mlink></ptxt></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YZ3K_05" category="10"><name>CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT</name><content5><atten3><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Inspect the fuses of circuits related to this system before performing the following inspection procedure.</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>After replacing the ECM, the new ECM needs registration (See page <mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000Z1DB"/></mlink>) and initialization(See page <mlink><xref label="Seep00002" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000YXU9"/></mlink>).</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>After replacing the fuel supply pump assembly, the ECM needs initialization.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00003" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000YXU9"/></mlink></ptxt></item><item><ptxt>After replacing an fuel injector, the ECM needs registration.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00004" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000Z1DB"/></mlink></ptxt></item></list1></atten3><atten4><ptxt>Read freeze frame data using the GTS. Freeze frame data records the engine condition when malfunctions are detected. When troubleshooting, freeze frame data can help determine if the vehicle was moving or stationary, if the engine was warmed up or not, and other data from the time the malfunction occurred.</ptxt></atten4></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YZ3K_01" category="01"><name>PROCEDURE</name><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0001" cellposition="1-1"><testtitle>READ VALUE USING GTS (STOP LIGHT SWITCH)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Enter the following menus: Engine and ECT / Data List / Stop Light Switch.</ptxt><gts-info category="data-list"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Data List</title><table type="data-list"><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Tester Display</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="item-name" args1="117"><ptxt>Stop Light Switch</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><gts-exec function-id="50003"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"><gts-pid pid-id="117"/></gts-ecu></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">2</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param-unit><app-param name="pid-id">117</app-param><app-param name="data-list-item-name">Stop Light Switch</app-param><app-param name="exception-process-id"/><app-param name="exception-process-div"/></app-param-unit></app-communication></gts-info></test1><test1><ptxt>Read the value displayed on the GTS when the brake pedal is depressed and released.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>OK</title><table><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.07in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="2.06in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Brake Pedal</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Display</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Released</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>OFF</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Depressed</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>ON</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="1-1"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="2-1" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0005"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result><result label="2" cellposition="1-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-2" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0002"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0002" cellposition="2-2"><testtitle>INSPECT STOP LIGHT SWITCH ASSEMBLY</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Inspect the stop light switch assembly.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" href="RM100000000G3FJ"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="2-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-2" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0003"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="2-4"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-4" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0008"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0003" cellposition="3-2"><testtitle>CHECK ECM (STP VOLTAGE)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the ECM connector.</ptxt><figure type="1" translate="C"><graphic graphicname="A275087C07" width="3.434793307in" height="4.677165354in"/><callout><table pgwide="0" type="caption-table"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="0.69in"/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.75in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>*a</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle"><ptxt>Brake Pedal Depressed</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>*b</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle"><ptxt>Brake Pedal Released</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>*c</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle"><ptxt>Component with harness connected</ptxt><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></callout></figure></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Measure the voltage according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt><spec type="voltage"><title>Standard Voltage</title><table><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.37in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Brake Pedal Condition</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry morerows="1" valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>A29-13 (STP) - Body ground</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Released</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>0 to 3 V</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Depressed</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>11 to 14 V</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-2" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0004"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="3-3"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-3" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0010"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0004" cellposition="4-2"><testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Replace the ECM.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" term-id-to="003" href="RM100000000FJHY"/><xref term-id-from="003" href="RM1000000013IGX"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="4-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="5-2" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0005"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0005" cellposition="5-2"><testtitle>CONFIRM WHETHER MALFUNCTION HAS BEEN SUCCESSFULLY REPAIRED</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Clear the DTCs.</ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-delete"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Clear DTCs</title><gts-exec function-id="50002"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param name="selected-state">1</app-param></app-communication></gts-info></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off for 30 seconds or more.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to ON and turn the GTS on.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Start the engine.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Accelerate the vehicle to 30 km/h (19 mph) or more, depress the brake pedal and decelerate the vehicle to 3 km/h (1.8 mph) or less 5 times or more.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Confirm that the DTC is not output again.</ptxt><atten4><ptxt>Perform the following procedure using the GTS to determine whether or not the DTC judgment has been carried out.</ptxt></atten4><test2><ptxt>Enter the following menus: Engine and ECT / Utility / All Readiness.</ptxt><gts-info category="utility-normal"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Utility</title><table type="utility"><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Tester Display</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="item-name" args1="20"><ptxt>All Readiness</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><gts-exec function-id="50005"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"><gts-util util-id="20"/></gts-ecu></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">4</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param-unit><app-param name="utility-id">20</app-param><app-param name="function-name">All Readiness</app-param></app-param-unit></app-communication></gts-info></test2><test2><ptxt>Input DTC P0724.</ptxt></test2><test2><ptxt>Check that STATUS is NORMAL.</ptxt><atten4><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>If STATUS is NORMAL, DTC judgment is complete and it can be determined that the system is normal.</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>If STATUS is INCOMPLETE or N/A, DTC judgment is incomplete. Perform the following procedure again 5 times: accelerate the vehicle to 30 km/h (19 mph) or more, depress the brake pedal and decelerate the vehicle to 3 km/h (1.8 mph) or less.</ptxt></item></list1></atten4></test2></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="5-2"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="6-2"><actiontitle>END</actiontitle><content6/></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0010" cellposition="4-3"><testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACE HARNESS OR CONNECTOR</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Repair or replace the harness or connector.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="4-3"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="5-3" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0005"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0008" cellposition="3-4"><testtitle>REPLACE STOP LIGHT SWITCH ASSEMBLY</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Replace the stop light switch assembly.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" href="RM100000000G3FH"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-4"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="4-4" childid="RM100000000YZ3K_01_0005"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp></subpara></para></ttl></section></servcat></pub></tmc-service-paragraph>